{"title":"Revamped Cervélo P-Series UCI TT & Tri Bike Gets French Painter-Inspired Limited Edition","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2024-cervelo-p-series-tt-tri-triathlon-bike-in-limited-edition-paris-green/","date":1732733092000,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P-Series-TT-Tri-Triathlon-bike-in-limited-edition-Paris-Green-1536x1024.webp\" width=\"1536\" height=\"1024\" alt=\"2024 Cervélo P-Series TT Tri Triathlon bike in limited edition Paris Green, angled\" /></p>\n<p>Cervélo just rolled out a flashy limited edition Paris Green P-Series time trial &amp; triathlon frame kit inspired by 19th-century French impressionist and post-impressionist painters. This new Cervélo P-Series is the brand’s more affordable TT &amp; tri bike, adapting much of the top-tier aero tech from their “fastest TT bike in the World Tour” for a broader audience, and now adding new features like internal storage and wider wheel and tire clearance.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>And this limited frameset comes with the new wide Reserve 52|63 wheels that the frame we optimized for in the wind tunnel, and bonus… with matching Paris Green graphics. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Oh, and I’m going to go out on a limb and say that it’s all yellow, not green.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Cervélo P-Series Paris Green limited edition TT &amp; triathlon bike</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P-Series-TT-Tri-Triathlon-bike-in-limited-edition-Paris-Green_complete-jpg.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1800\" height=\"1080\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P-Series-TT-Tri-Triathlon-bike-in-limited-edition-Paris-Green_complete-jpg.webp\" alt=\"2024 Cervélo P-Series TT Tri Triathlon bike in limited edition Paris Green, complete bike side\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P-Series-TT-Tri-Triathlon-bike-in-limited-edition-Paris-Green_complete-jpg.webp 1800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P-Series-TT-Tri-Triathlon-bike-in-limited-edition-Paris-Green_complete-297x178.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P-Series-TT-Tri-Triathlon-bike-in-limited-edition-Paris-Green_complete-1536x922.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P-Series-TT-Tri-Triathlon-bike-in-limited-edition-Paris-Green_complete-120x72.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P-Series-TT-Tri-Triathlon-bike-in-limited-edition-Paris-Green_complete-768x461.webp 768w\" /></a><figcaption>(Photos/Cervélo)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>OK, let’s get this straight. Cervélo is calling the limited edition P-Series color Paris Green because it “<em>takes inspiration from an arsenic-based<br />pigment developed in the 19th century… used by Georges Seurat and Claude Monet, among others, to render vivid natural scenes in oil paintings.</em>” So those masters of French painting used it to render hard to reproduce greens. Albeit, it seems like Wikipedia thinks that Paris Green is a lot more green than this at best acid green Cervélo P-series.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><div>\n\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Completely off-topic, but bike industry interesting… <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Paris_green\" target=\"_blank\">Paris Green</a> pigment (<em>originally classified as the world’s first chemical insecticide</em>) was invented in Schweinfurt, Germany where SRAM has its <a href=\"https://www.sram.com/en/zipp/media/sram-germany\" target=\"_blank\">German engineering HQ</a> and where tech like the latest Zipp hubs were developed. And that includes the Zipp ZR1 hubs in the limited edition wheels that come with this special frame kit.  </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Kinda weird fun fact.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>OK, so the 2024 P-Series is completely new!</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P-Series-TT-Tri-Triathlon-bike-in-limited-edition-Paris-Green_angled-jpg.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1000\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P-Series-TT-Tri-Triathlon-bike-in-limited-edition-Paris-Green_angled-jpg.webp\" alt=\"2024 Cervélo P-Series TT Tri Triathlon bike in limited edition Paris Green, angled bike\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P-Series-TT-Tri-Triathlon-bike-in-limited-edition-Paris-Green_angled-jpg.webp 1500w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P-Series-TT-Tri-Triathlon-bike-in-limited-edition-Paris-Green_angled-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P-Series-TT-Tri-Triathlon-bike-in-limited-edition-Paris-Green_angled-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P-Series-TT-Tri-Triathlon-bike-in-limited-edition-Paris-Green_angled-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P-Series-TT-Tri-Triathlon-bike-in-limited-edition-Paris-Green_angled-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P-Series-TT-Tri-Triathlon-bike-in-limited-edition-Paris-Green_angled-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Here’s the thing. Earlier this summer Cervélo revamped both their top-tier P5 and more affordable P-Series UCI-approved time trial and triathlon bikes. It happened during the time trial stage when we were at Eurobike. And Cervélo also was not at Eurobike. So I missed both updates until now.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P-Series-TT-Tri-Triathlon-bike-in-limited-edition-Paris-Green_new-frameset-side-scaled.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1536\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P-Series-TT-Tri-Triathlon-bike-in-limited-edition-Paris-Green_new-frameset-side-scaled.webp\" alt=\"2024 Cervélo P-Series TT Tri Triathlon bike in limited edition Paris Green, frameset\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P-Series-TT-Tri-Triathlon-bike-in-limited-edition-Paris-Green_new-frameset-side-scaled.webp 2560w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P-Series-TT-Tri-Triathlon-bike-in-limited-edition-Paris-Green_new-frameset-side-297x178.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P-Series-TT-Tri-Triathlon-bike-in-limited-edition-Paris-Green_new-frameset-side-1536x922.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P-Series-TT-Tri-Triathlon-bike-in-limited-edition-Paris-Green_new-frameset-side-120x72.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P-Series-TT-Tri-Triathlon-bike-in-limited-edition-Paris-Green_new-frameset-side-768x461.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P-Series-TT-Tri-Triathlon-bike-in-limited-edition-Paris-Green_new-frameset-side-2048x1229.webp 2048w\" /></a><figcaption>LTD Paris Green frameset</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>This new <a href=\"https://www.cervelo.com/en-US/bikes/p-series\" target=\"_blank\">P-Series</a> is a pretty big departure from the previous generation, as it moves closer to the range-topping P5. It still has a more conventional front end and maintains mechanical drivetrain compatibility with external cable routing entering behind the headset and a standard 1 1/8″ round steerer interface for standard stem &amp; bar setups. But the whole seat cluster got reshaped to make for smoother airflow down into wide-set seatstays, and the same around wider fork legs. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P-Series-TT-Tri-Triathlon-bike-in-limited-edition-Paris-Green_new-Reserve-front-and-rear-specific-52-63-aero-carbon-wheels-jpg.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P-Series-TT-Tri-Triathlon-bike-in-limited-edition-Paris-Green_new-Reserve-front-and-rear-specific-52-63-aero-carbon-wheels-jpg.webp\" alt=\"2024 Cervélo P-Series TT Tri Triathlon bike in limited edition Paris Green, new Reserve 52|63 aero wheels\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P-Series-TT-Tri-Triathlon-bike-in-limited-edition-Paris-Green_new-Reserve-front-and-rear-specific-52-63-aero-carbon-wheels-jpg.webp 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P-Series-TT-Tri-Triathlon-bike-in-limited-edition-Paris-Green_new-Reserve-front-and-rear-specific-52-63-aero-carbon-wheels-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P-Series-TT-Tri-Triathlon-bike-in-limited-edition-Paris-Green_new-Reserve-front-and-rear-specific-52-63-aero-carbon-wheels-1536x1024.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P-Series-TT-Tri-Triathlon-bike-in-limited-edition-Paris-Green_new-Reserve-front-and-rear-specific-52-63-aero-carbon-wheels-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P-Series-TT-Tri-Triathlon-bike-in-limited-edition-Paris-Green_new-Reserve-front-and-rear-specific-52-63-aero-carbon-wheels-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P-Series-TT-Tri-Triathlon-bike-in-limited-edition-Paris-Green_new-Reserve-front-and-rear-specific-52-63-aero-carbon-wheels-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P-Series-TT-Tri-Triathlon-bike-in-limited-edition-Paris-Green_new-Reserve-front-and-rear-specific-52-63-aero-carbon-wheels-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Cervélo optimized all of it around wider 52mm deep x 25mm internal front &amp; 63mm deep x 24mm internal rear Reserve wheels fitted with 29mm Vittoria Corsa tires to go faster – and save a claimed 3.5W. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P-Series-affordable-carbon-TT-Tri-Triathlon-bike_front-end-detail-jpg.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1333\" height=\"1000\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P-Series-affordable-carbon-TT-Tri-Triathlon-bike_front-end-detail-jpg.webp\" alt=\"2024 Cervélo P-Series UCI-approved time trial &amp; triathlon bike updated, front end detail\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P-Series-affordable-carbon-TT-Tri-Triathlon-bike_front-end-detail-jpg.webp 1333w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P-Series-affordable-carbon-TT-Tri-Triathlon-bike_front-end-detail-297x223.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P-Series-affordable-carbon-TT-Tri-Triathlon-bike_front-end-detail-120x90.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P-Series-affordable-carbon-TT-Tri-Triathlon-bike_front-end-detail-768x576.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P-Series-affordable-carbon-TT-Tri-Triathlon-bike_internal-storage-glovebox-hatch-detail-jpg.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1333\" height=\"1000\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P-Series-affordable-carbon-TT-Tri-Triathlon-bike_internal-storage-glovebox-hatch-detail-jpg.webp\" alt=\"2024 Cervélo P-Series UCI-approved time trial &amp; triathlon bike updated, internal storage detail\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P-Series-affordable-carbon-TT-Tri-Triathlon-bike_internal-storage-glovebox-hatch-detail-jpg.webp 1333w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P-Series-affordable-carbon-TT-Tri-Triathlon-bike_internal-storage-glovebox-hatch-detail-297x223.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P-Series-affordable-carbon-TT-Tri-Triathlon-bike_internal-storage-glovebox-hatch-detail-120x90.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P-Series-affordable-carbon-TT-Tri-Triathlon-bike_internal-storage-glovebox-hatch-detail-768x576.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P-Series-affordable-carbon-TT-Tri-Triathlon-bike_headtube-detail-jpg.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1333\" height=\"1000\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P-Series-affordable-carbon-TT-Tri-Triathlon-bike_headtube-detail-jpg.webp\" alt=\"2024 Cervélo P-Series UCI-approved time trial &amp; triathlon bike updated, headtube detail\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P-Series-affordable-carbon-TT-Tri-Triathlon-bike_headtube-detail-jpg.webp 1333w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P-Series-affordable-carbon-TT-Tri-Triathlon-bike_headtube-detail-297x223.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P-Series-affordable-carbon-TT-Tri-Triathlon-bike_headtube-detail-120x90.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P-Series-affordable-carbon-TT-Tri-Triathlon-bike_headtube-detail-768x576.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>At the same time, the new P-series also adds internal frame storage through a hatch under the downtube water bottle mount (but loses previous aero bottle compatibility).</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P-Series-affordable-carbon-TT-Tri-Triathlon-bike_standard-Ultegra-Di2-complete-bike-build-jpg.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P-Series-affordable-carbon-TT-Tri-Triathlon-bike_standard-Ultegra-Di2-complete-bike-build-jpg.webp\" alt=\"2024 Cervélo P-Series UCI-approved time trial &amp; triathlon bike updated, complete with Shimano Di2 and Reserve carbon wheels\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P-Series-affordable-carbon-TT-Tri-Triathlon-bike_standard-Ultegra-Di2-complete-bike-build-jpg.webp 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P-Series-affordable-carbon-TT-Tri-Triathlon-bike_standard-Ultegra-Di2-complete-bike-build-297x178.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P-Series-affordable-carbon-TT-Tri-Triathlon-bike_standard-Ultegra-Di2-complete-bike-build-1536x922.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P-Series-affordable-carbon-TT-Tri-Triathlon-bike_standard-Ultegra-Di2-complete-bike-build-120x72.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P-Series-affordable-carbon-TT-Tri-Triathlon-bike_standard-Ultegra-Di2-complete-bike-build-768x461.webp 768w\" /></a><figcaption>P-Series Ultegra Di2</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Standard P-series framesets without wheels start at $3000. Then, complete P-series TT/tri bikes start at $3950 with mechanical 105 and go up to $7300 with Ultegra Di2 on those premium Reserve wheels like shown above.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Also a new Cervélo P5 in 2024, too</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P5-time-trial-triathlon-UCI-race-bike_Visma-Lease-a-Bike-team-racing-jpg.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1800\" height=\"1080\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P5-time-trial-triathlon-UCI-race-bike_Visma-Lease-a-Bike-team-racing-jpg.webp\" alt=\"2024 Cervelo P5 time trial triathlon UCI race bike, racing\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P5-time-trial-triathlon-UCI-race-bike_Visma-Lease-a-Bike-team-racing-jpg.webp 1800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P5-time-trial-triathlon-UCI-race-bike_Visma-Lease-a-Bike-team-racing-297x178.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P5-time-trial-triathlon-UCI-race-bike_Visma-Lease-a-Bike-team-racing-1536x922.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P5-time-trial-triathlon-UCI-race-bike_Visma-Lease-a-Bike-team-racing-120x72.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P5-time-trial-triathlon-UCI-race-bike_Visma-Lease-a-Bike-team-racing-768x461.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Yes, the 2024 Cervélo P5 is new, too. But the changes are less dramatic. The older version that we covered all the way <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/all-new-cervelo-p5-adds-disc-brakes-and-more-speed-remains-uci-legal/\" target=\"_blank\">back in 2019</a>, was really just updated last summer with a slightly smoother ‘fastback’ seat cluster and bigger 34mm tire clearance – both for improved rider comfort. And both features that the new P-series inherits, as well. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P5-time-trial-triathlon-UCI-race-bike_TT-Tri-bike-frameset-frame-kit-jpg.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1800\" height=\"1080\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P5-time-trial-triathlon-UCI-race-bike_TT-Tri-bike-frameset-frame-kit-jpg.webp\" alt=\"2024 Cervélo P5 time trial triathlon UCI-approved TT Tri race bike, frameset\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P5-time-trial-triathlon-UCI-race-bike_TT-Tri-bike-frameset-frame-kit-jpg.webp 1800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P5-time-trial-triathlon-UCI-race-bike_TT-Tri-bike-frameset-frame-kit-297x178.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P5-time-trial-triathlon-UCI-race-bike_TT-Tri-bike-frameset-frame-kit-1536x922.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P5-time-trial-triathlon-UCI-race-bike_TT-Tri-bike-frameset-frame-kit-120x72.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P5-time-trial-triathlon-UCI-race-bike_TT-Tri-bike-frameset-frame-kit-768x461.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The front end does get stiffer with simplification, the base bar gets a bit lower, and vertical adjustability of the aerobars increases to compensate. And Cervélo gives the top P5 a bigger 61cm size to match the wider 6-size range already offered on the more affordable P-series.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In the end, it all adds up to a claimed 1W aerodynamic improvement. And that climbs 4W more when paired with new wide Reserve 77|88 wheels with 29mm Vittoria tires, much like the shallower wheels on the P-series</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P5-time-trial-triathlon-UCI-race-bike_SRAM-Red-AXS-complete-TT-Tri-bike-jpg.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2400\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P5-time-trial-triathlon-UCI-race-bike_SRAM-Red-AXS-complete-TT-Tri-bike-jpg.webp\" alt=\"2024 Cervélo P5 time trial triathlon UCI-approved TT Tri race bike, SRAM Red AXS complete bike\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P5-time-trial-triathlon-UCI-race-bike_SRAM-Red-AXS-complete-TT-Tri-bike-jpg.webp 2400w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P5-time-trial-triathlon-UCI-race-bike_SRAM-Red-AXS-complete-TT-Tri-bike-297x165.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P5-time-trial-triathlon-UCI-race-bike_SRAM-Red-AXS-complete-TT-Tri-bike-1536x853.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P5-time-trial-triathlon-UCI-race-bike_SRAM-Red-AXS-complete-TT-Tri-bike-120x67.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P5-time-trial-triathlon-UCI-race-bike_SRAM-Red-AXS-complete-TT-Tri-bike-768x427.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P5-time-trial-triathlon-UCI-race-bike_SRAM-Red-AXS-complete-TT-Tri-bike-2048x1137.webp 2048w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Pricing is a lot higher on the more integrated and electronic-only P5. The 2024 Cervélo P5 frameset (including cockpit &amp; seatpost) sells for $6000, the ‘cheapest’ complete build with Ultegra Di2 for $10,000, and the top-end Dura-Ace Di2 or Red AXS models for $13,500.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Cervélo P-Series Paris Green LTD – Pricing &amp; availability</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P-Series-TT-Tri-Triathlon-bike-in-limited-edition-Paris-Green_LTD-frame-kit-jpg.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2500\" height=\"1500\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P-Series-TT-Tri-Triathlon-bike-in-limited-edition-Paris-Green_LTD-frame-kit-jpg.webp\" alt=\"2024 Cervelo P-Series TT Tri Triathlon bike in limited edition Paris Green, frame kit\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P-Series-TT-Tri-Triathlon-bike-in-limited-edition-Paris-Green_LTD-frame-kit-jpg.webp 2500w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P-Series-TT-Tri-Triathlon-bike-in-limited-edition-Paris-Green_LTD-frame-kit-297x178.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P-Series-TT-Tri-Triathlon-bike-in-limited-edition-Paris-Green_LTD-frame-kit-1536x922.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P-Series-TT-Tri-Triathlon-bike-in-limited-edition-Paris-Green_LTD-frame-kit-120x72.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P-Series-TT-Tri-Triathlon-bike-in-limited-edition-Paris-Green_LTD-frame-kit-768x461.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P-Series-TT-Tri-Triathlon-bike-in-limited-edition-Paris-Green_LTD-frame-kit-2048x1229.webp 2048w\" /></a><figcaption>2024 Cervelo P-Series limited edition Paris Green frame kit</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>This bright Paris Green (<em>yellow</em>) <a href=\"https://www.cervelo.com/en-US/bikes/p-series\" target=\"_blank\">limited edition frame kit</a> sells for $5500, and includes the newly updated 2024 Cervélo P-Series frameset – frame, fork, headset &amp; seatpost (no bar or stem) – plus a matched set of aero carbon Reserve 52|63 wheels built on Zipp ZR1 SS hubs (and both XDR &amp; HG freehub bodies).</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P-Series-TT-Tri-Triathlon-bike-in-limited-edition-Paris-Green_with-SRAM-Rival-AXS-jpg.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1800\" height=\"1000\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P-Series-TT-Tri-Triathlon-bike-in-limited-edition-Paris-Green_with-SRAM-Rival-AXS-jpg.webp\" alt=\"2024 Cervelo P-Series TT Tri Triathlon bike in limited edition Paris Green, complete\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P-Series-TT-Tri-Triathlon-bike-in-limited-edition-Paris-Green_with-SRAM-Rival-AXS-jpg.webp 1800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P-Series-TT-Tri-Triathlon-bike-in-limited-edition-Paris-Green_with-SRAM-Rival-AXS-297x165.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P-Series-TT-Tri-Triathlon-bike-in-limited-edition-Paris-Green_with-SRAM-Rival-AXS-1536x853.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P-Series-TT-Tri-Triathlon-bike-in-limited-edition-Paris-Green_with-SRAM-Rival-AXS-120x67.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-Cervelo-P-Series-TT-Tri-Triathlon-bike-in-limited-edition-Paris-Green_with-SRAM-Rival-AXS-768x427.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Only 500 of the special edition Paris Green TT/Tri frame kit will be sold. And they are available in the broad 6-size range (48-61cm) of the P5. So, get yours by reaching out now to your local Cervélo dealer. Then, sort out your own unique build kit like this SRAM Rival AXS setup!</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.cervelo.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><em>Cervelo.com</em></a></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2024-cervelo-p-series-tt-tri-triathlon-bike-in-limited-edition-paris-green/\">Revamped Cervélo P-Series UCI TT &amp; Tri Bike Gets French Painter-Inspired Limited Edition</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Cory Benson","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"897f54bc4511fbce5f7fe0b9832ae74286a280fa17526c547f04cafe22b435eb","category":"Cycling"}